plugin

:source ~/.vimrc

PlugInstall
- vim管理:        " https://github.com/junegunn/vim-plug
- 启动插件:       " https://github.com/mhinz/vim-startify
- 命令行插件:     " https://github.com/vim-airline/vim-airline
- 缩进线:        " https://github.com/Yggdroot/indentLine
- 配色方案:      " https://github.com/sickill/vim-monokai
- 搜索快速定位:   " https://github.com/easymotion/vim-easymotion
- 文件目录:      " https://github.com/scrooloose/nerdtree
- 文件搜索:      " https://github.com/ctrlpvim/ctrlp.vim

- 添加surround   " https://github.com/tpope/vim-surround
  normal: 
  ds: delete surround {ds <existing char>}, e.g., "test" -> ds"-> test
  cs: change surround {cs <existing char> <desired char>}, e.g., "test" -> cs"' -> 'test' ... cs"t 123> -> <123>test</123>
  ys: you add surround: {ys <motion> <desired char>},e.g., test -> ys iw" -> "test"

- 模糊搜索与替换   " https://github.com/junegunn/fzf.vim
  :??? Ag [PATTERN] 模糊搜索字符串
  :Files [PATH] 模糊搜索目录

- 代码注释:      " https://github.com/tpope/vim-commentary
  单行注释:gc,取消单行注释gcgc; 
  多行注释及取消: V selection -> gc
  
- vs code vim
https://github.com/VSCodeVim/Vim

1. 使用easy-motion, <leader><leader>s<char>
2. 使用gb -> multi-cursor use <esc> to switch mode, <ctrl>+c to jump
   使用gh -> find definition and error report
   使用gd -> function definition
   
